ode_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI5MTU3NTI4", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/29157528?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007", "html_url": "https://github.com/kemu3007", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "assignees": [{"login": "kemu3007", "id": 29157528, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI5MTU3NTI4", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/29157528?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007", "html_url": "https://github.com/kemu3007", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}], "milestone": null, "comments": 0, "created_at": "2022-05-03T02:57:37Z", "updated_at": "2022-05-05T01:04:38Z", "closed_at": null, "author_association": "OWNER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "\r\n\r\nPyCon US 2022でPyScriptについての発表があったので流れに乗り、とりあえずPyodideを手元で触ったので紹介します。\r\n\r\n[New from Anaconda: Python in the Browser](https://www.anaconda.com/blog/pyscript-python-in-the-browser)\r\n\r\n## PyodideをCDN経由でインポート\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<head>\r\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/pyodide/v0.20.0/full/pyodide.js\"></script>\r\n</head>\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Pythonスクリプトの実行\r\n\r\n`const pyodide = await loadPyodide();` で初期化処理を行なっており、`pyodide.runPython` でスクリプトの実行を行います。\r\n\r\n`runPython`の戻り値はスクリプトファイル内部で最後に評価された値です。\r\n\r\nパッケージのインポートに関しては動作確認中\r\n\r\n- ファイル構成\r\n\r\n```markdown\r\n- index.html\r\n- scripts/\r\n  - get_version.py\r\n  - get_zen.py \r\n```\r\n\r\n- `index.html`\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<h2>Python: <span id=\"python-version\"></span></h2>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div id=\"python-zen\"></div>\r\n\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\nasync function setScriptValue(pyodide, dir, tag) {\r\n  const script = await (await fetch(dir)).text()\r\n  document.getElementById(tag).innerText = pyodide.runPython(script)\r\n}\r\nasync function main(){\r\n    const pyodide = await loadPyodide();\r\n    setScriptValue(pyodide, \"scripts/get_zen.py\", \"python-zen\")\r\n    setScriptValue(pyodide, \"scripts/get_version.py\", \"python-version\")\r\n}\r\nmain();\r\n</script>\r\n```\r\n\r\n- `scripts/get_zen.py`\r\n\r\n```python\r\nimport io\r\nfrom contextlib import redirect_stdout\r\n\r\nstdout = io.StringIO()\r\n\r\nwith redirect_stdout(stdout):\r\n    import this\r\n\r\nstdout.getvalue()\r\n```\r\n\r\n- `scripts/get_version.py`\r\n\r\n```python\r\nimport sys\r\n\r\nf\"{sys.version_info.major}.{sys.version_info.minor}.{sys.version_info.micro}\"\r\n```\r\n## 表示される画面\r\n\r\nZen of Pythonが表示されている、実行環境は3.10.2らしい。\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29157528/166849852-d2d81146-baa4-4fc7-a697-4e083e2135a3.png)\r\n\r\n## 利用可能なライブラリ\r\n\r\nデフォルトで以下のライブラリが利用可能、scikit-learnなども含まれているので今度動作確認を行う。\r\n\r\nhttps://pyodide.org/en/stable/usage/packages-in-pyodide.html\r\n\r\n## コードとテストページ\r\n\r\n今回利用したコードは[こちら](https://github.com/kemu3007/pyodide-sample)、作成したページは[こちら](https://kemu3007.github.io/pyodide-sample/)から確認することができます。", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/40/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/40/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}